t/become-an-outreachy-mentor-support-the-growth-and-diversity-of-the-ocaml-=
community/8213">
https://discuss.ocaml.org/t/become-an-outreachy-mentor-support-the-growth-a=
nd-diversity-of-the-ocaml-community/8213</a> contains some more information=
 about being a mentor which you may want to take a look at.
